1387
01:11:14,770 --> 01:11:18,315
People don't see how we catch seafood,

1388
01:11:18,399 --> 01:11:20,859
they only care for consumption.

1389
01:11:20,943 --> 01:11:26,740
A lot of the seafood we're consuming today
