1403
01:12:24,840 --> 01:12:26,925
<i>I was sad to be leaving Thailand
so suddenly,</i>

1404
01:12:27,009 --> 01:12:30,012
<i>knowing there were young men just like me
trapped on fishing boats</i>

1405
01:12:30,095 --> 01:12:31,638
<i>who'd never be able to go home.</i>

1406
01:12:31,722 --> 01:12:35,351
<i>But after risking our safety,
