1504
01:21:11,992 --> 01:21:14,077
<i>Just like dolphins and whales,</i>

1505
01:21:14,160 --> 01:21:16,329
<i>fish can also have complex social lives,</i>

1506
01:21:16,413 --> 01:21:19,791
<i>even teaming up with other species
