1507
01:21:19,875 --> 01:21:23,587
<i>With research proving, once and for all,
the intelligence, memory capabilities,</i>

1508
01:21:23,670 --> 01:21:25,213
<i>and sentience of these animals,</i>

1509
01:21:25,297 --> 01:21:28,258
<i>fish, and even crustaceans,
