01:21:38,101 --> 01:21:40,395
sense of touch, sense of smell and taste.

1515
01:21:40,478 --> 01:21:42,606
They have the right kind of pain receptors

1516
01:21:42,689 --> 01:21:45,901
for physical, chemical,
